6163 // It does this by inserting an insertvalue for each element in the resulting
6164 // struct, as opposed to just inserting a single struct. This will only work if
6165 // each of the elements of the substruct are known (ie, inserted into From by an
6166 // insertvalue instruction somewhere).
6167 //
